stimulusHtml: What is the value of result after the code segment is executed if x has the value 15 and y has the value 5?

features.html:
Consider the following code segment, which uses properly declared and initialized int  variables x and y and the String variable result.

 

String result = "";
if (x < 5)
{
   if (y > 0)
   {
      result += "a";
   }
   else
   {
      result += "b";
   }
}
else if (x > 10)
{
   if (y < 0)
   {
      result += "c";
   }
   else if (y < 10)
   {
      result += "d";
   }
   result += "e";

result += "f";
